    ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
    ║   User Interface Library  —  Stellar  v5.0              ║
    ║   "Lean & Modern" — major restructure                    ║
    ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

    CHANGELOG (v5.0 — Lean & Modern Edition):

    ── PHILOSOPHY ───────────────────────────────────────────
    Less surface area, sharper components. v5 removes anything
    that nobody used in real admin / executor scripts, and
    invests the saved lines in things that change daily DX:
    state binding, a builder API, profiles, new components.

    ── REMOVED  ─────────────────────────────────────────────
    • Dead code: Pulse, CrossFade, Lift, Bounce easing,
      GetFlags(), IsConsole, SetTheme custom-table.
    • Niche components: CodeBlock, Paragraph, TabBadge,
      Maximize button, SearchableDropdown, Section collapse,
      HexInput, Blur HTTP module.
    • Light theme palette (all themes are now dark variants;
      admin tools overlay live game lighting → dark wins).
    • Toggle effect over-stacking — only glow + spring knob now
      (was glow + spring + ripple + hover, 4 effects per click).

    ── ADDED  ───────────────────────────────────────────────
    • STATE SYSTEM (new):
        local power = State.new(50)
        slider = section:Slider{ State = power }
        power:Get(); power:Set(80); power:OnChanged(fn)
      Multiple components can bind to the same State and stay
      synced. Foundation for forms, dirty tracking, derived UI.

    • BUILDER API (new):
        local tab = window:Tab{ Title = "Main", Icon = "..." }
        local sec = tab:Section{ Title = "Combat" }
        sec:Toggle{ Title = "Auto-aim", Default = false }
        sec:Slider{ Title = "FOV",  Min = 0, Max = 360 }
      Returns the controller chain; the old Cfg.Tab pattern
      still works for backwards compatibility.

    • THEME PRESETS (new):  Default, Midnight, Tokyo, Mocha
      All are dark. Switch with Options:SetTheme("Tokyo").

    • DENSITY MODE (new):  Compact / Comfortable
      Compact = power users; Comfortable = mobile-first.
      Adjusts all component heights + padding globally.

    • SetAccent(color) (new): one-call accent override that
      propagates to every accent-coloured node in the window.

    • COMPONENTS (new):
        :RadioGroup{Options=..., Default=...}    -- 1-of-N
        :Stepper{Min, Max, Step, Default}         -- +/- buttons

    • PROFILE SYSTEM (new):
        Options:SaveProfile("PvP")
        Options:LoadProfile("PvP")
        Options:ListProfiles() → { "Default", "PvP", "Farm" }
        Options:SetAutoSave(true) -- debounced auto-save on change

    ── INHERITED FROM v3/v4  ────────────────────────────────
    Per-window state, InputHub, TweenManager, FAB, haptics,
    tooltips, confirm modal, animations module, full bug-fix
    audit (drag/keybind/slider/dropdown leaks), mobile touch
    zones, ColorPicker, full theme engine with per-window cache.

